data.description: PRICE REDUCED. Priced to sell.....  Welcome to this newer beautiful and spacious home built in 2020 in the desirable Seasons at Community Ranch.  This beauty features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, and a large loft that can be used as an office, game room, or 5th bedroom.  This beautiful open floor plan offers a bright and airy living room with, a dining area, and a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a large pantry.  The master suite boasts a massive walk in closet, dual sinks, and separate shower.  The backyard is ideal for entertaining with a large cement patio slab for barbecuing and entertaining.  The home also offers tank less water heater, solar panels (not leased) and a spacious 2 car garage. This newer home and community is perfectly located for convenient shopping, near schools, dining, freeways and much more.  Don't miss this opportunity to own this stunning home in a excellent community.....
